            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指回升162點報25842點 商米登場高開2.92倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段反彈，恒生指數開市報25842點，升162點或0.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4878點，升51點或1.07%；國企指數以8700點開市，升55點或0.64%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260129_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報128.8元，升1.82%；騰訊(00700)開報474.6元，升0.17%。滙控(00005)開報140.6元，暫時無升跌；友邦(01299)開報84.25元，升1.32%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">企業首季業績陸續出爐，績後股價表現榮辱互見。比亞迪電子(00285)季度純利大跌逾95%，該股今早開報24.52元，挫6.56%，創52周新低；同系比亞迪(01211)首季盈利跌逾55%，該股今早開報104.4元，升0.68%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/00285-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"比亞迪電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/00285-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">比亞迪電子官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)首季營運利潤升7.6%，該股今早開報61.25元，升2%。中石化(00386)季度盈利升26.9%，該股今早開報4.64元，升1.09%；中海油(00883)首季多賺7.1%，該股今早開報28.9元，跌0.28%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外電報道指，美國商務部指示多間晶片設備公司暫停向華虹半導體(01347)供貨；該股今早開報109.6元，跌6.27%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，商米科技(06810)今日掛牌，以97.5元開市，較招股價24.86元高2.92倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15936104-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87162%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125842%e9%bb%9e-%e5%95%86%e7%b1%b3%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 09:29:26",
