            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">官方今日公佈人民幣兑美元中間價報6.8608，較上日中間價下調19個點子。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上日中間價6.8589，下午4:30官方收市價6.8360，夜市收市價6.8372。</p>\n</div>",
